This is an ai agent that can book appointments by communicating with the users. The app is linked with the google calendar associated with the given Mail ID. 
It schedules meetings and events and can also be used to set reminders and also check out the upcoming schedules that are set.



#Ensure that the following is installed.
INSTALL BACKEND:-
pip install fastapi uvicorn "langchain-google-genai>=0.0.9" python-dotenv google-api-python-client google-auth-httplib2 google-auth-oauthlib dateparser python-dotenv
INSTALL FRONTEND :-
pip install streamlit requests

#To run the application use the following.
RUN BACKEND :-
uvicorn main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000

RUN FRONTEND :-
cd frontend
streamlit run app.py
